name: expect error — unknown vocabulary import
description: Verifies that importing a vocabulary that was not supplied produces a semantic error.
tags: compile, error

# Provide one vocab but import a different (nonexistent) one.
# The compiler must throw and the error message must mention the missing name.
vocab_inline ecommerce: ```
Kind: order is a thing.
Property: id of order is a string.
```

source_inline: ```
---
vocabulary: mystery.merconfig
---
To run:
  complete.
```

expect_compile: fail
expect_error_kind: semantic
expect_error_contains: mystery
